Rattrap:





Rattrap stopped to watch a persuit take place. It was against a snow 
leopard and a flier. He could hear him up from the canopy. His ears 
picked that up. He watched the cat, and she was heading his 
direction. He ducked down behind a log and pinned his ears back.
